      1602,
      1078,
      1847
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} \\text{Ta có: } \\int_{0}^{1/12} L'(t) dt &= 70^\\circ - 10^\\circ = 60^\\circ \\\\ \\Leftrightarrow \\int_{0}^{1/12} k \\cdot e^{-0,22t} dt &= 60^\\circ \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{k}{0,22} \\left(1 - e^{-0,22/12}\\right) = 60^\\circ \\Leftrightarrow k \\approx 729 \\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
